# Manual Changes Required for "Completed without Reason" Category

## 1. lib/services/churnService.ts

### Change 1: Line ~210 - Update the completed logic
FIND:
```typescript
      if (completed) {
        acc.completed++;
        return acc;
      }
```

REPLACE WITH:
```typescript
      if (completed) {
        // Check if completed without a proper churn reason
        if (!hasCompletedReason && (hasCompletedStatus || hasThreeCalls)) {
          acc.completedWithoutReason++;
        } else {
          acc.completed++;
        }
        return acc;
      }
```

