### Change 5: Line ~275 - Add filter case for completedWithoutReason
FIND:
```typescript
        if (filter === 'completed') {
          return completed;
        }
```

REPLACE WITH:
```typescript
        if (filter === 'completed') {
          return completed && hasCompletedReason;
        }
        
        if (filter === 'completedWithoutReason') {
          return completed && !hasCompletedReason && (hasCompletedStatus || hasThreeCalls);
        }
```

